text: Anneliese Seonbuchner was a hurdler from Germany. Seonbuchner competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. She was born on 13 September 1929 and died on 20 November 2020.Anneliese Seonbuchner == References == Category:1929 births Category:2020 deaths Category:German hurdlers Category:Olympians for Germany
